{"tid":784594,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 失業癈中西藏遊","createTime":"2018-08-18T13:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:54:52.000Z","uid":197783,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4e3ece28e5213cdca1f971869726a9bd86631e","tid":784594,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"依幾年都地獄式OT, 一日做十幾個鐘. 前排終於炒左老闆魷魚 , 可以整理返依幾年去完旅行未處理既相片.<br />\n<br />\n好羨慕年青既巴打可以徒步/踩車去旅行,我依D 上左年紀有家室既. 極其量只會自駕遊, 今次分享既係西藏包車殘廢餐之旅. <br />\n<br />\n其實去西藏包車司機係極無聊既一件事, 每日都上車落車, 十幾個鐘起架車入面, 加上空氣稀薄 好易入睡, 訓足全程. 但係果度D 路,我真係冇信心應付. 特別係起缺氧咁易訓著既環境揸車.<br />\n<br />\n事前準備:<br />\n我只係準備左Diamox, 同埋D 防寒衣物, 睡袋.  <br />\n<br />\nDiamox 係必需品,如果冇Diamox 我應該提早返香港, 事關我一到拉薩已經有高山反應. 因為我要乾淨,所以睡袋係必需, 有個睡袋訓覺暖好多.<br />\n<br />\n今次行程主要係:<br />\n<br />\n⁠拉薩-日喀則-珠峰大本營-神山岡仁波齊-札達土林-古格王國-羊八井-納木錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/212804_322ab8fec9b0b8176acc2a9869a36ad4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F212804_322ab8fec9b0b8176acc2a9869a36ad4.JPG&h=04ea31df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9日入面行左3千5公里.最低海拔3千6米.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n包車大約千三蚊人仔一日."},{"pid":"8ae9691bd78f91068f70f3bc77daa33d549d48e8","tid":784594,"uid":190739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"劉明睇野"},{"pid":"00a621bb38460316e7f44d89a86629d9b333ef1a","tid":784594,"uid":56782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"lm g持"},{"pid":"a66920968cb8019e1667d583b6e8d81c3252b39d","tid":784594,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"我係由重慶入去拉薩, 中午去到拉薩,一早就已經打算抖三日黎做適應, 落機時頭果個鐘都冇乜野,諗緊有冇需要留三日, 結果一搬完行李入房就開始黎料. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/214843_57cba854dd672f06b6c1ee1238d044c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F214843_57cba854dd672f06b6c1ee1238d044c4.jpg&h=c12417cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一Check 個SpO2. 低過80%. (正常香港係98-99%) 有D 頭赤赤. 乜都唔理,訓覺先.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/214852_9c055e4829b7bd3155c1d7b4812ec391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F214852_9c055e4829b7bd3155c1d7b4812ec391.jpg&h=8b5b73f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訓到夜晚九點幾,都好似冇乜起色,個頭仲愈來愈痛, 因為身體需要泵更多氧氣,所以心跳一路都維持九十幾. 結果同行友人就幫我出去藥房買傳說中既高原安 &amp; 高原康 &amp; 紅景天. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高原安其實係D 中藥成份, 高原康係西藥成份,網上D 人講到係軍方藥物冇國家醫藥管理局審批, take at your own risk.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/214904_3717b3cfe1bad1f2b9ffe098de409f1e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F214904_3717b3cfe1bad1f2b9ffe098de409f1e.JPG&h=b36b15e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/214907_a50f5a5096f679f43f6c69c141d769f5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F214907_a50f5a5096f679f43f6c69c141d769f5.JPG&h=2c10f6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高原安冇乜效果,食剩一粒 , 高原康就食哂一盒.<br />\n<br />\n實測過Diamox + 高原康係有效既, 一唔舒服食完就好快見效.<br />\n高原安就算罷啦,如果你真係高山反應到就黎頂唔順, 高原安應該救唔到你一命.<br />\n<br />\n最後紅景天, 同飲夏枯草清熱一樣,信則有,不信則無. 我試完覺得完全冇料到. (我香港有預先飲定紅景天,去到又有食過紅景天膠囊) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起酒店訓左2日, 2日夾埋起碼訓左30個鐘.   果度D 酒店房好多都有放濕機, 因為真係乾燥得好緊要, 我同行友人仲帶左個USB 迷你放濕, 加幾滴精............<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">油</span>, 放起床頭好訓好多.<br />\n<br />\n同埋一定要帶唇膏!   我就係大意冇帶,最後都要起當地買返支."},{"pid":"be491a9a063fa3049ae230230190e660a3b0d37e","tid":784594,"uid":197783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:17:10.000Z","msg":"第3日真係舒服左好多, 出街活動都冇不適.<br />\n其實起市區都係去八廓街,布達拉宮依D 例牌行程.<br />\n<br />\n不多講,放相算了! <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為要去布達拉宮,所以我地早一日去買飛. 一早去到條龍其實冇乜人, 市前上網刨過文又話要搵旅行社又話上網站買.  我地一於少理,寧願早D去排隊  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/220721_8bf3689f5a865cae35213130bac8bb9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F220721_8bf3689f5a865cae35213130bac8bb9d.jpg&h=60e84c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n售票處附近有間氧吧,不過冇時間冇去考究入面有乜設施. 我貪得意買左罐氧吸一兩口, 但係發現之後個依賴感會令你更加不適. 所以之後全程都冇吸到.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/221230_e875c090313c6d432df83db5280dd529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F221230_e875c090313c6d432df83db5280dd529.jpg&h=f8e3a6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八廓街入面其實都冇乜特別野行, 但係感受下佢地D 信仰係一個唔錯既地方,因為之後我去既路線唔會見到咁多人.  所以依1-2日起市區要影多D 人.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/221610_f4beb1cc9d8c2facd4a8b8710066e106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F221610_f4beb1cc9d8c2facd4a8b8710066e106.jpg&h=df5e2964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/221611_495ff1629d9e30e94a11448daa59fa83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F221611_495ff1629d9e30e94a11448daa59fa83.jpg&h=0236a4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/221611_403df75ff74c612491d70370117c2e03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F221611_403df75ff74c612491d70370117c2e03.jpg&h=ef8e5d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/221612_ea71a33df8cf02b87da649b280d16543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F221612_ea71a33df8cf02b87da649b280d16543.jpg&h=9886c91c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大昭寺外係最多人拜既地方,今年2月有火燭,不過事後問過當地人,損毀唔嚴重.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/221622_474d004f30762bc09677143479cfb889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F221622_474d004f30762bc09677143479cfb889.jpg&h=b149dc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/221623_522fd9fbc106c479e5005903159611ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F221623_522fd9fbc106c479e5005903159611ef.jpg&h=dbd970be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e67ed5e8ec7e04f7676a01e97e6ae7b1dabd5d8b","tid":784594,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5a00ab96f6649828948c7fa61d6fe3505300d17","tid":784594,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:31:15.000Z","msg":"好多旅遊書都有介紹既甜茶館, 入到去人頭湧湧, D 本地人好驚我地拎相機出黎影相. 所以我都係影下D 野食就算,一路食又有D 小乞兒行埋黎見你遊客就討錢.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/013053_277d118f9c2bb378aef2744a23c7a40f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F013053_277d118f9c2bb378aef2744a23c7a40f.JPG&h=61650adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杯茶其實幾好飲, D 藏麵又平又好食.  係薯條炸到過哂火...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/013046_08edcae063a83f658d673d8fa054053b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F013046_08edcae063a83f658d673d8fa054053b.JPG&h=76e778b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行上布達拉宮條路都幾多石級, 分2-3次終於上到去. 景觀好開揚.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/002951_343cf56875fd68cf18a2ea2f62cc780f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F002951_343cf56875fd68cf18a2ea2f62cc780f.JPG&h=b726da51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實遠晀先感覺到宏偉, 上到去除左D 佛像好靚之外,其實感覺都唔算太深刻, D 房間好多都係烏燈黑火<br />\n<br />\n行左一陣就去到白宮.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/013105_57e4be3d26baddaa78d3b4bc9dc5bcc5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F013105_57e4be3d26baddaa78d3b4bc9dc5bcc5.JPG&h=1cdab80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白宮係布達拉宮內喇嘛居住既地方,廣場地面係用西藏特有的一種風化石阿嘎土造。"},{"pid":"6bb8e8ac6df9fd8bfcf8b5886b93c2a05764ff4e","tid":784594,"uid":197783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"D人話影布達拉宮最佳位置係對面既藥王山, 依個位好多當地人起度影結婚相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/194001_9aca499473fdb2b9b08e1c6ef590515b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F194001_9aca499473fdb2b9b08e1c6ef590515b.JPG&h=501f5694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎個新娘都相當有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/194125_2c74e2a22cce6441cfa8bc34686b67fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F194125_2c74e2a22cce6441cfa8bc34686b67fd.jpg&h=cbdaf7b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/194129_b5a7227067f01c0206cd7c4bba77a7ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F194129_b5a7227067f01c0206cd7c4bba77a7ae.jpg&h=523fc795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/194139_45e1e62fae481b80ef8f6ef1855a764e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F194139_45e1e62fae481b80ef8f6ef1855a764e.JPG&h=e74bcfff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前既人仔50蚊, 我諗90後好多都未見過, 十幾年前上大陸果陣仲有流通,不過張張都舊到好似梅菜咁. 新版依張為左要插旗哂馬,所以用布達拉宮做背面既圖案."}]}